Вакансія від 20 березня 2020
QA Analyst (eCommerce Dept)
Gameloft
IT;
250–1000 співробітників
Харків
Повна зайнятість.
Досвід роботи від 1 року.
Опис вакансії
Ensure the quality of WAP, WEB sites, test game’s builds and other e-Commerce systems by verifying and reporting failures to meet defined Gameloft standards to provide best product in a shortest timeline. QA is the first and the last team who see sites before user starts surf them, so we’ll have the greatest opportunity to check just created new sites, buy first created games and be the first in GL structure with product approval.Key Responsibilities:• Verifying WAP, WEB sites and other e-Commerce systems, by following the specifications and the project design that he receives (storyboard, particular test instructions) • Reporting results in a clear and complete manner, so that the final project will not contain any errors, functionality and design issues or other deviations from the basic requirements or from the standards that applies in the eCommerce department.Expected knowledge and qualifications:• Strong knowledge of using mobile platforms and willing to learn new ones.• Experienced user of MS Office, Open Office, Google Docs and Mozilla Thunderbird email client• Knowledge of main principles and logic of WAP, WEB sites.• Previous working experience with Redmine is plus• Knowledge of MantisBT system is a plus• Intermediate (or upper) level of English (mails, instant messengers)Additional skills and abilities:• Strong willing to break any system in any possible way. • Out of box, analytical mind. • The ability to learn complex frameworks and procedures with ease, good memory.• Should be independent and willing to take responsibilities.• Ability to sustain quality work even under stress.• Ability to deal with routine work.• Very good communications skills.
